	measure DPO = ```
			
			 Var Days = 365
			 Var AccountPayables = CALCULATE(
			    SUM('vendorLedgerEntries'[remainingAmount]),
			    vendorLedgerEntries[open] = true,
			    DATESBETWEEN(vendorLedgerEntries[postingDate], [TodayLocal] - 365 ,[TodayLocal])
			)*-1
			 Var COGS = CALCULATE(SUM('generalLedgerEntries'[amount]), 'generalLedgerEntries'[accountCategory] = "Cost of Goods Sold",
			 DATESBETWEEN( generalLedgerEntries[postingDate], [TodayLocal] - 365 ,[TodayLocal]))
			 RETURN
			 If(AccountPayables = 0, "--", FORMAT(Divide(AccountPayables,COGS)*Days,0))
			```
		displayFolder: AccountPayableMeasures
		lineageTag: bdc9616e-1816-418a-8b8c-51ee7cfad519

