	column DueCategory = ```
			
			Var TodayDate = [TodayLocal]
			VAR DueDate= vendorLedgerEntries[dueDate]
			Return
			SWITCH(
			    TRUE(),
			    ISBLANK(DueDate), "No Due Date",
			    DueDate < TodayDate , "Overdue",
			    DueDate = TodayDate, "Due today",
			    DueDate > TodayDate && DueDate <= TodayDate + 30, "Due next 30 days",
			    DueDate > TodayDate + 30 && DueDate <= TodayDate + 60, "Due next 60 days",
			    DueDate > TodayDate + 60 && DueDate <= TodayDate + 90, "Due next 90 days",
			    DueDate > TodayDate + 90, "Due next >90 days"
			)
			 
			```
		displayFolder: AccountPayableMeasures
		lineageTag: 1b05346b-481f-4776-9590-40054875cb84
